    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿过 《零号门》，回到公元 30 年左右的犹地亚和加利利，开启一场充满故事的冒险。时间来到反乌托邦的 2072 年，一个全球极权政权掌控并审查一切信息——凡是与政权的“真相”不符的东西都被禁止。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演马克斯（Max），一名孤儿。在祖母因藏有一本被禁的历史书而被捕后，他意外发现了父母留下的时光机。而这本书，正是政权想要抹去的《圣经》。<br><br>探索古代以色列，亲身经历祖母只能偷偷讲述的故事，亲眼见证耶稣的事工。你会逛热闹的集市、探访历史遗迹、结识圣经中的传奇人物，并感受到政权为掩盖真相而不择手段的残酷。<br><br>为了修复时光机并回到家乡，你需要完成任务、躲避追捕、破解谜题，揭开真理。击败罗马的压迫，在“世界之间”的领域对抗邪恶力量，并找到拯救祖母、历史和未来的方法！<br><br>本作由虚幻引擎 5 打造，注重历史细节与真实感，带来沉浸式的体验，让各个年龄层的玩家都能亲身感受人类历史上最关键的时刻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >剧情丰富的动作冒险</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入马克斯的世界，对抗邪恶的 UniFi 政权。在拯救祖母的旅程中，揭开 UniFi 篡改历史对几代家庭造成的影响。马克斯能否揭露他们的阴谋，还是历史会继续被操控？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748280/extras/71864b71e0f8d7d0a1968208d749f8c4.poster.avif?t=1770652251\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748280/extras/71864b71e0f8d7d0a1968208d749f8c4.webm?t=1770652251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748280/extras/71864b71e0f8d7d0a1968208d749f8c4.mp4?t=1770652251\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关键使命</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在绝望的未来，马克斯意外穿越到公元一世纪，被困在守护真理的路上。为了拯救自己和祖母，他必须完成任务、解谜，并与邪恶势力战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748280/extras/371eb50b347d135e1cca6e320ef0ca0e.poster.avif?t=1770652251\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748280/extras/371eb50b347d135e1cca6e320ef0ca0e.webm?t=1770652251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748280/extras/371eb50b347d135e1cca6e320ef0ca0e.mp4?t=1770652251\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>穿越古代以色列</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由虚幻引擎 5 精心制作，重现了古迦百农、迦拿、约旦河等经典地点。制作团队曾参与《荒野大镖客》《刺客信条》《侠盗猎车手》等知名游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748280/extras/d89861ea4e018603875798dc7cdeab62.poster.avif?t=1770652251\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748280/extras/d89861ea4e018603875798dc7cdeab62.webm?t=1770652251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748280/extras/d89861ea4e018603875798dc7cdeab62.mp4?t=1770652251\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >第一视角体验圣经</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入犹地亚和加利利的世界与文化，探索考证严谨的圣经地标与事件。亲身感受古代以色列的城市生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748280/extras/5ce35f06cdc4cc6c631b8c3a1e54cef6.poster.avif?t=1770652251\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748280/extras/5ce35f06cdc4cc6c631b8c3a1e54cef6.webm?t=1770652251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748280/extras/5ce35f06cdc4cc6c631b8c3a1e54cef6.mp4?t=1770652251\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >发掘圣经中略写的人物</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >圣经中只简短提到过他们，而在 《零号门》 里，你将深入了解这些人与耶稣相遇的故事，以及是什么让他们走向祂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748280/extras/e3cdddf0d50335ddf6890d271b30dce9.poster.avif?t=1770652251\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748280/extras/e3cdddf0d50335ddf6890d271b30dce9.webm?t=1770652251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1748280/extras/e3cdddf0d50335ddf6890d271b30dce9.mp4?t=1770652251\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
